Title: Surveying the Cliffside
Description:
Nothing like brisk ocean air to get you in the mood to dig!

We're standing in the rubble of an ancient dragonkin fishing village. These dragonkin were ancestors of the blue dragonkin that live on the island today. Humble as it is, the remote location means it's gone relatively undisturbed by treasure hunters.

If there's anything left that hasn't fallen into the sea, we'll find it!
ObjectivesText: Speak with Roska to start the dig then excavate artifacts from the cliffside.

Objectives.Text: Tell Roska to start the dig
